         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Finance Plan To Report
Process Group: DC Manage Accounting and Control Data
Process: DC-030-120B Close Period - Non GR_R1</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B5E0EA71-0924-457B-863F-D984B847DAC5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Note:
- Restriction at CC &amp; PC level on workdays will be handled through JE Approval Workflow
- Detailed process will be in Functional Specification document FPRE0407_CFIN, FPRE0407_IP, FPRE0407_IF
- S4 HANA system is IP &amp; IF system. This process execution will be in all three system (IP, IF &amp; CFin system).</text>
      </textAnnotation>
